casebody.data:
BALDWIN v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 48,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided February 5, 1965.

Before Prescott, C. J., and Hammond, Horney, Sybert, Oppenheimer and Barnes, JJ.

PER Curiam.

For the reasons assigned by Judge Parker in his opinion below, the application will be denied.

Application denied.
